ts for monks and why?</span><hr size=1> I dunno I have heard many different stories, but I was always lead to believe that Str is the most important stat- along with AC of course- then what?<br>
<br>
Correct me if I have been mislead, thx la~ <p>Sujittra Thongloh <br>
